所有涨幅。 &lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;—&lt;/em&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/MsBxdLcatoRN1-lAM5el_SHxyY3oFGlqDswdKovdpNIBiK2LKbfaHTKzcxP4tUEV1i9evNtJRAbuD06SLLCnp6EoHDOjMf7lA32n0EbSXKusTSPIUIG05PcUm2tYH44ROEFqQPqQ6tlCn68kH30uullLRu3xXr8OlUfhEx3Z_J4XAfgEvCmUwGuvf0M_cHTL7t85EMNYgeybYvuXzx6bAFuao6yqwnvA9PhSxKG-GlIMi8rUGjM6ilxzPyWvydGobaZblKoJAWbmlk_YL0HitDjvXzYnUz5QLNp5jwChIV59js-94BgEIXarkvuuy1mFeb8Z3P_j6_bP7iS_lC3XrtdgLFlkZF2RyRSeK_dn73hRulAWnrJ_hliyFnZYYK12x7ZqG14dFVtBzGXB6siRfl0xXc8Gs5dgqtIKXUlqS9XVIRBZBHgWJxCB4zFFPEi7jmyw1YtM18H--lEZWCVD/srZ5U6R33g1yakjhVlrFXRCfaOT1sRhj/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="David Rovella - 总编辑：Bloomberg Digital |彭博社"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;David E. Rovella&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;h3 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;今天您需要了解什么&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;摩根大通周四&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/LM3OCDj7wHnFQ9ZDGO9jHHlYVJv6XkFDcvgFD5fJ_zVQnBtl_ePDJAlQPLPGiXYKvOd5JUJJsK7N3E6nKpmusPW8MO4V6PAizv1VrDeEDLLRFuBYK5cg_3QRoiS2P19FzOWu127cWwDtZ5CwvjgNdJWrtqswB0zxrd_O1ZDoP0ugGKD9TfBrahf9HefO4VAXQcVeEGew2Aj6CK1aZeR-3nUdC5_eeXnj8EpQOi26m3EgsAlhSKhDB-VGZx4ORPRx8npTFTywuX0QIOTBy-JGDidvqKtk7ynro8q17DjiSyQRgUqp6jzeXEFTd_eJTSfrpAWwGucwCDCtgvM-YF-GhePuWTO8LK6PuCTYeEoosv-9NK6crPGsFK7R9X30_6pSUfok5G23yADjpCTdHeMB1kP6JUeIQxxKl2feugPhB3YOI1T--HxoZW6IyQANVuQ-kURmQQpHPp_gB4Uz1j1uvmnYX3RXpPW21Ko-ELbOG9rcOVxErZUTHRz45tLIfzlnOCREDvw7iuhPDCxcBkKFIN2mFuNNnASrGvJNTf5p8WhacEOu/8QZ6TCb0Mn70lkncQEiG2yoY5hVVKg_2/22" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="摩根大通希望聘请明星交易撮合者、资深交易员作为戴蒙继承人"&gt;在消费者银行业务主管玛丽安·莱克(Marianne Lake)突然离职后&lt;/a&gt;任命特洛伊·罗尔博(Troy Rohrbaugh)和道格·佩特诺(Doug Petno)为联席总裁&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;，震惊了华尔街&lt;/strong&gt;。这些戏剧性的举动颠覆了业界猜测谁将接替首席执行官杰米·